          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-2">Comprehensive security review and hardening pass across the entire platform. UUID validation on all route parameters, XSS prevention in template rendering, API key scope enforcement (read-only keys can no longer perform write operations), Zod input validation on every endpoint, and CORS tightened for production. Draft OOS content is now properly access-controlled, and ticket data is scoped to authenticated organizations.</p>
        </div>

