          <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Background Similarity Computation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-2">Claim similarity analysis now runs asynchronously after publishing. Previously, the O(n*m) comparison blocked the publish response as the network grew. Publishing is now instant regardless of how many claims exist across the platform, while similarities still compute and store in the background.</p>
        </div>

